  "body": "<p>Studio Calico's <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/34th-street-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">34th Street December kit</a> is still available. Every month when I get the kits, I have a little routine that I go through. Here is how this layout came together using the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/34th-street-scrapbook-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">main kit only</a>. The firs thing I do is open up the main kit and spread everything out. I like to flip the papers to my favorite sides facing up so I can choose which ones to use.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600317832012-3A3HC54N5YWJUKMVHGOX/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Then I gather my favorite tools, including the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/other-tools/brad-setter-and-piercing-tool?aff=6cc2c70f\">Brad Setter from We R Memory Keepers</a> and the BEST WHITE PEN ever made, aka <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/pens-markers/uni-ball-white-pen?aff=6cc2c70f\">Uniball Signo</a>.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600317847714-DUVGFT7YRP7KC935VLXS/13b-1-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I lay it all out, choose photos and begin the fun process of piecing it all together.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13c-41-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600317965756-XYB8GIHLPJURQCVQMYDM/13c-41-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"13d-8-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600317888746-5XBHX5E2RG5VQZLKMVVC/13d-8-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n\n\n<p>I made some splatter with the mists that I wasn't too happy with. No big deal, because I just placed my photo right over it.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13e-9-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600318031253-GOENP4DB4PM1XKF047QA/13e-9-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13f-9a-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600318003899-1I7AQYK0C1N3CF4NCF67/13f-9a-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13g-9b-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600318004499-U4RV6X7W9ZXTHQYJKB63/13g-9b-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13h-9c-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600318004604-L5U4GRTOWGV0LB0H50HM/13h-9c-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13i-9d-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600318006700-2JA149M7SL24D7EOZAKB/13i-9d-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13j-9e-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600318007208-SLMDIJWAOH2ED6KAMFRZ/13j-9e-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13k-9f-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600318007408-853E31XSWLN3L7STT1UF/13k-9f-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13l-9g-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600318007969-C83OUG0B3N8R0GMVW936/13l-9g-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13m-DownUnderSC-449x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600318008192-C05P10NM3KN64LBH1S8V/13m-DownUnderSC-449x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Hope you enjoyed seeing the layout come together. You can see all that I created with the December kits in <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/design-team-gallery/34th-street-scrapbook-kit/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">my gallery</a>.</p>"
